@startuml
title Activity Diagram - Full Order Lifecycle

|Customer|
start
:Be seated at table;

|Waiter|
:Take order;
:Add items to order;

|System|
:Create Order;
:Send to Kitchen Queue;

|Kitchen|
:Receive order;
:Start preparation;
:Mark as Ready;

|Waiter|
:Serve food to customer;

|Customer|
:Finish meal;
:Request bill;

|Waiter|
:Request bill generation;

|System|
:Generate Bill;
:Apply pricing strategy;
:Calculate tax and total;

|Cashier|
:Present bill to customer;
:Receive payment;
:Mark bill as paid;

|System|
:Log order to history;
:Clear table;

stop
@enduml
